[Name] GoboHide
[Summary] Hide/Unhide a directory or symlink
[Description] GoboHide is an userland application that effectively implements "hidden files" on Linux. It requires a kernel patch, available for download at https://github.com/gobolinux/Recipes/tree/master/trunk/Linux
[License] GNU General Public License version 2
[Homepage] http://gobolinux.org/?page=doc/articles/gobohide
